# Structure and Naming Rules

- Place HTTP features under `src/api/<actor>/<feature>/`.
- Keep data-access logic in `_repositories/**`.
- Keep shared logic in `src/common/**`.
- Follow existing naming conventions:
  - `*.controller.ts`
  - `*.service.ts`
  - `*.module.ts`
  - `dto/*.dto.ts`
- Reuse existing helpers/services before creating duplicate utilities.
